<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00115</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT RECOGNIZING, PROTECTING AND STRENGTHENING THE INDIGENOUS PEOPLES AND LOCAL COMMUNITIES CONSERVED AREAS AND TERRITORIES, ACKNOWLEDGING THEIR CONTRIBUTION TO BIODIVERSITY CONSERVATION AND PROTECTION OF KEY BIODIVERSITY AREAS, ESTABLISHING FOR THE PURPOSE THE NATIONAL ICCA REGISTRY, APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SHORT TITLE : Indigenous Peoples And Local Communities Conserved Areas And Territories (icca) Act Of 2016</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Declares it a policy of the State to pursue sustainable development, recognition of the rights of Indigenous Cultural Communities/Indigenous Peoples (ICCs/IPs), biodiversity conservation and climate change mitigation and adaptation.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>BAGUILAT, TEDDY JR. BRAWNER</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2016-06-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>NATURE : Welfare</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Lazatin (016 2016-08-30)</td><td>2. Savellano (018 2016-09-05)</td><tr><td>3. Villanueva (021 2016-09-13)</td><td>4. Robes (021 2016-09-13)</td><tr><td>5. Bordado (056 2016-12-14)</td><td>6. Teves (056 2016-12-14)</td><tr><td>7. Turabin-Hataman (078 2017-03-06)</td><td>8. Yap (V.) (000 2018-02-26)</td><tr><td>9. Nieto (000 2018-03-05)</td><td>10. Sangcopan (000 2018-01-31)</td><tr><td>11. Belmonte (R.) (000 2018-02-20)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON INDIGENOUS CULTURAL COMMUNITIES AND INDIGENOUS PEOPLES ON 2016-07-26</td></tr></table>